        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4305",
        "content": "They have the common property of causing irritation and inflammation of the eyes, throat, and air passages, and may cause spasm of the glottis, bronchitis, and pneumonia.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
