        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4305",
        "content": "The chief vegetable purgatives are aloes, colocynth, gamboge, jalap, scammony, seeds of castor oil plant, croton oil, elaterium, the hellebores, and colchicum.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
