        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4305",
        "content": "Certain of these irritant poisons exert a marked influence on the central nervous system, as the following:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
